_sText:
This is the beta version of my second map cs_cul_de_sac.  T's start behind the house with the hostages.  CT's start behind the house across the street.  

This map is recommended for about 20 to 32 players but supports up to 64.  

By the final version, this map will support HDR and have radar.

I'm looking for any constructive feedback on the map.

(BTW my clan tag is -=|C.P.O.K.W.D.W.H|=- if you are wondering after looking under the map)
